- **Catalysts ahead:** TSM earnings Apr 16, defense primes (RTX/NOC/LMT) Apr 21-23, FOMC Apr 29, AAPL earnings ~Apr 30.
- **Bias:** Neutral with bullish lean — the tape wants to rally but CPI is a potential trap door.
